  <title>GObject.signal_add_emission_hook</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function signal_add_emission_hook(signal_id: Number, detail: GLib.Quark, hook_func: GObject.SignalEmissionHook): Number {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_signal_add_emission_hook()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds an emission hook for a signal, which will get called for any emission
of that signal, independent of the instance. This is possible only
for signals which don't have #G_SIGNAL_NO_HOOKS flag set.</p>

